data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated home in the desirable Wynnefield neighborhood! This stunning property offers a perfect blend of modern upgrades and classic charm. With 3 bedrooms and ample living space, this home is designed to accommodate a comfortable and contemporary lifestyle.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and bright living area, featuring stylish hardwood floors and large windows that fill the space with natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating an inviting atmosphere for entertaining guests or enjoying family meals.  The heart of the home is the fully updated kitchen, boasting sleek countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space for all your culinary needs. From the kitchen, step out onto the deck, where you can relax and unwind while enjoying your morning coffee or hosting outdoor gatherings.  The master bedroom is a true retreat, complete with an on-suite bathroom for added convenience and privacy. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized, offering ample closet space and flexibility for various needs such as a home office or guest room. The two full bathrooms are beautifully renovated, featuring modern fixtures and finishes.  Convenience is key with this home, as it includes not one, but two powder rooms—one on the first floor and another in the completely finished basement. This additional living space in the basement provides endless possibilities, whether you envision a home theater, game room, or home gym.  Parking will never be an issue, thanks to the driveway and street parking options. The beautifully landscaped front yard adds to the curb appeal of this already impressive property.  Located in the sought-after Wynnefield neighborhood, this home offers easy access to local amenities, parks, schools, and transportation options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this renovated gem your new home sweet home. Schedule a showing today!
